ZH: 我雇了一个保姆照顾我的孩子。
EN: I hired a nanny to take care of my children.

ZH: 年轻夫妇需要雇一个保姆帮忙做家务。
EN: Young couples need to hire a maid to help with household chores.

ZH: 保姆每天都会准时到家来照顾老人。
EN: The nanny comes to take care of the elderly at home every day on time.

ZH: 学校里的保姆会负责学生的健康和安全。
EN: The nanny at the school is responsible for the health and safety of students.

ZH: 这家公司为员工提供免费的保姆服务。
EN: This company provides free nanny services for its employees.

ZH: 请务必签订合同，与保姆明确责任和薪酬。
EN: Be sure to sign a contract with the nanny to clarify responsibilities and salary.

ZH: 她已经找了一个有经验的保姆来照顾她的宠物。
EN: She has hired an experienced nanny to take care of her pets.

ZH: 保姆会帮忙做饭、清洁和洗衣。
EN: The nanny helps with cooking, cleaning, and laundry.

ZH: 我的邻居雇了一名年轻保姆照看孩子。
EN: My neighbor hired a young nanny to look after her children.

ZH: 保姆必须具备相关的培训和资质。
EN: Nannies must have relevant training and qualifications.

ZH: 公司的福利包括生育假和保姆津贴。
EN: The company's benefits include maternity leave and nanny allowance.

ZH: 她已经和保姆建立了良好的信任关系。
EN: She has established a good trust relationship with the nanny.

ZH: 我们需要一名全职保姆来照顾家中的婴儿。
EN: We need a full-time nanny to take care of the baby at home.

ZH: 她用自己的积蓄雇了一个保姆帮忙看家。
EN: She used her savings to hire a nanny to help with housekeeping.

ZH: 如果需要，保姆可以协助孩子完成作业。
EN: The nanny can help children with their homework if needed.

ZH: 保姆通常会跟随家庭一起度过节假日。
EN: Nannies usually spend holidays with the family.

ZH: 请确保你对保姆支付足够的薪水。
EN: Make sure you pay the nanny enough salary.

ZH: 学校的保姆会监督学生的课外活动。
EN: The school's nanny supervises students' extracurricular activities.

ZH: 保姆需要处理家庭日常的琐事和急需问题。
EN: Nannies need to deal with the daily trivial matters and urgent issues of the family.

ZH: 我们感谢保姆在我们的家中的辛勤工作。
EN: We are grateful for the hard work of the nanny in our home.
